    <h1>Deleted Repositories</h1>

    <ul class="breadcrumb">
        <li><a href="index.html">Dashboard</a></li>
        <li>Deleted</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="meta">Repositories absent from a successful inventory sweep in <code>TestOrg</code>.</p>

    
    <p class="meta">No deleted repositories detected.</p>
    

    
    <h2>Acknowledged owner anomalies</h2>

    <p class="meta">CODEOWNERS-referenced owners in <code>TestOrg</code> that are not a resolvable GitHub team — acknowledged and surfaced, not deleted or hidden.</p>

    
    <h3>Wildcard owners</h3>

    <p class="meta">Glob-shaped CODEOWNERS owners (e.g. <code>@org/*</code>) — a catch-all/default-owner construct, not a configured team.</p>

    <div class="table-wrapper">
        <table class="data-table" data-sortable>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col" data-sort-type="text">Owner <span class="tooltip-trigger tooltip-trigger-header" tabindex="0" data-tooltip="CODEOWNERS owner token that is glob-shaped, not a resolvable GitHub team.">ⓘ<span class="sr-only">CODEOWNERS owner token that is glob-shaped, not a resolvable GitHub team.</span></span></th>
                    <th scope="col" data-nosort>Referencing Repositories <span class="tooltip-trigger tooltip-trigger-header" tabindex="0" data-tooltip="Repositories whose CODEOWNERS file names this wildcard owner.">ⓘ<span class="sr-only">Repositories whose CODEOWNERS file names this wildcard owner.</span></span></th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                
                <tr>
                    <td>@TestOrg/*</td>
                    <td>beta-repo</td>
                </tr>
                
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    

    
    <h3>Ghost teams</h3>

    <p class="meta">GitHub teams referenced by CODEOWNERS in <code>TestOrg</code> that GitHub no longer has.</p>

    <div class="table-wrapper">
        <table class="data-table" data-sortable>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col" data-sort-type="text">Team <span class="tooltip-trigger tooltip-trigger-header" tabindex="0" data-tooltip="GitHub team slug that a CODEOWNERS file still references, but GitHub has deleted (404 on roster fetch).">ⓘ<span class="sr-only">GitHub team slug that a CODEOWNERS file still references, but GitHub has deleted (404 on roster fetch).</span></span></th>
                    <th scope="col" data-nosort>Referencing Repositories <span class="tooltip-trigger tooltip-trigger-header" tabindex="0" data-tooltip="Repositories whose CODEOWNERS file still names this deleted team.">ⓘ<span class="sr-only">Repositories whose CODEOWNERS file still names this deleted team.</span></span></th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                
                <tr>
                    <td><a href="https://github.com/orgs/TestOrg/teams/team-a" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">team-a</a></td>
                    <td>alpha-repo, beta-repo</td>
                </tr>
                
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    
    

</body>

